@startuml
autonumber

skinparam BoxPadding 10
skinparam ParticipantPadding 10
skinparam defaultFontSize 20
skinparam maxMessageSize 400

actor "Admin Sistem" as Admin
boundary "UI Tempat Sampah" as UI
control "Controller" as Controller
database "DB" as DB

== 1. Akses Menu & Auto-Cleanup ==
Admin -> UI : Buka menu Tempat Sampah
UI -> Controller : Ambil data sampah
activate Controller
Controller -> DB : Query data terarsip (produk, penjualan, dll)
Controller -> DB : Pembersihan otomatis data kedaluwarsa (> 30 hari)
DB --> Controller : Data ter-update
Controller --> UI : List data sampah
deactivate Controller

== 2. Pemulihan & Penghapusan Manual ==
Admin -> UI : Pilih item untuk dipulihkan/dihapus
alt Aksi: Pulihkan
    Admin -> UI : Klik Restore
    UI -> Controller : Kirim permintaan pemulihan data
    Controller -> DB : Pulihkan status data menjadi aktif
else Aksi: Hapus Permanen
    Admin -> UI : Klik Purge
    UI -> Controller : Kirim permintaan penghapusan permanen
    Controller -> DB : Hapus permanen data & relasi
end

Controller --> UI : Konfirmasi Berhasil
UI --> Admin : Refresh data list
@enduml